\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
PI_{Fisher}=\sqrt{PI_{Laspeyres}\cdot PI_{Paasche}}\approx1.016
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Compensation=|PI_{Fisher}-1|\cdot w=192<|CV|,
\]

\end_inset

but this is not generally the case for all price increases.
 
