\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

exact
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 EV? We don't want to use approximation using the Slutsky equation here.
 What we want to use is:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
v(\vec{p}^{0},w+EV) & = & v(\vec{p}^{1},w)\\
\frac{(260+EV)(6+8)}{6\cdot8} & = & \frac{260\cdot(5+12)}{5\cdot12}\\
\therefore EV & \approx & -7.4286
\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset


