\series default
\shape default
 Since 
\begin_inset Formula $v(\cdot)$
\end_inset

 is stictly concave, 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}^{*}>x_{2}^{*}$
\end_inset

 iff 
\begin_inset Formula $v'(x_{1}^{*})<v'(x_{2}^{*})$
\end_inset

, which occurs iff 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{p_{1}}{p_{2}}<1$
\end_inset

 or 
\begin_inset Formula $p_{1}<p_{2}$
\end_inset

.
 
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\end_layout

